data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value: Starting: Each player is dealt 6 cards each once the last card has been dealt the top card is pulled and placed under the deck. This card is the trump card and will be used throughout the game but first it is used to find the games first attacker. The player with the lowest rank matching the trump suit will be first!

data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Defending Phase: The goal for the defender is to place cards that are of the same suit but a higer rank than what the attacker has played if the defender does not have a matching suit they can place a trump suit of any rank to defend. If the defender is successful in defending against 6 attacks or if the attacker can no longer attack then the round is done and the cards are sent to the discard pile and the defender becomes the attacker for the next round. If the defender can not defend then they must TAKE the cards in the field and they stay as the defender for the next round.

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Attacking Phase: The goal for the attacker is to make the defender pick up the cards in the middle. First attack the attacker may place any card subsequent attacks the attacker must play a rank that has already been played by either them or the defender. If the attacker can not place a card then they must PASS and the round is finished and the cards are sent to the discard pile and they become the defender, however if the attack is successful then the defender must pick up all of the cards on the field and they stay as the attacker for the next round.
